            <article eId="article-1">
                <num>1</num>
                <heading>Citation, commencement and interpretation</heading>
                <paragraph eId="article-1-1">
                    <num>1</num>
                    <content>
                        <p>This Order may be cited as the Mental Health (Scotland) Act 2015 (Commencement No. 3) Order
                            2017 and comes into force on 5th May 2017.
                        </p>
                    </content>
                </paragraph>
                <paragraph eId="article-1-2">
                    <num>2</num>
                    <content>
                        <p>In this Order “the 2015 Act” means the Mental Health (Scotland) Act 2015.</p>
                    </content>
                </paragraph>
            </article>
